1
00:00:34,708 --> 00:00:35,875
Finally.

2
00:00:35,958 --> 00:00:39,625
I finally got my power back.

3
00:00:39,708 --> 00:00:41,791
Once my demonic liver has fully grown,

4
00:00:41,875 --> 00:00:46,541
I will be unstoppable!

5
00:00:47,333 --> 00:00:52,458
AGENT FROM ABOVE

6
00:00:53,166 --> 00:00:57,166
TURNING THE WHEEL

7
00:01:15,375 --> 00:01:16,208
Han Chieh.

8
00:01:16,916 --> 00:01:18,041
What's wrong?

9
00:01:20,708 --> 00:01:23,125
Wu Tien-chi said
he put a demonic liver inside me.

10
00:01:24,041 --> 00:01:25,708
It isn't inside you anymore.

11
00:01:27,125 --> 00:01:28,208
Then why aren't I…

12
00:01:29,416 --> 00:01:30,375
I gave you mine.

13
00:01:42,958 --> 00:01:44,791
I'm the Third Crown Prince's agent.

14
00:01:45,416 --> 00:01:46,458
I can't die.

15
00:01:48,125 --> 00:01:49,750
One of the perks of the job.

16
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:54,791
The doctor said my cancer
has already spread.

17
00:01:54,875 --> 00:01:57,333
I only have a few months left to live.

18
00:01:57,833 --> 00:02:00,791
You shouldn't waste your energy on me.

19
00:02:01,916 --> 00:02:04,000
I should've died over ten years ago.

20
00:02:04,791 --> 00:02:06,541
Every extra day is a gift.

21
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:08,875
I got more than I deserved.

22
00:02:15,083 --> 00:02:16,041
Han Chieh.

23
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,750
Can you win this time?

24
00:02:27,833 --> 00:02:29,125
When I win,

25
00:02:30,208 --> 00:02:31,458
We'll go back to the tree.

26
00:02:46,666 --> 00:02:50,041
The Demon King has regained his power.
I'm going to find him.

27
00:02:50,125 --> 00:02:51,958
-Take care of Leafy.
-I'll help you.

28
00:02:52,041 --> 00:02:54,583
How? You don't stand a chance
against that thing.

29
00:02:54,666 --> 00:02:56,916
I could at least
get a few rounds off at him.

30
00:02:57,416 --> 00:03:00,625
Take care of the neighbors and Leafy.
I'm counting on you.

31
00:03:19,416 --> 00:03:20,666
DONGFENG MARKET

32
00:03:47,291 --> 00:03:49,750
You're really something else,
you little punk.

33
00:03:49,833 --> 00:03:51,416
Still standing

34
00:03:51,916 --> 00:03:53,958
even without a liver.

35
00:03:54,541 --> 00:03:56,125
Once you get the demonic liver,

36
00:03:56,208 --> 00:04:00,166
physical pain like this
will be a distant memory.

37
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:03,333
When that happens,
I doubt I'll still be human.

38
00:04:03,416 --> 00:04:04,375
I'm warning you.

39
00:04:04,458 --> 00:04:08,375
If you don't let the others go,
I won't let you put that liver inside me.

40
00:04:12,583 --> 00:04:16,708
You never planned on letting me
do it, did you?

41
00:05:25,625 --> 00:05:27,708
Nine Dragons Divine Fire Barrier.

42
00:05:28,250 --> 00:05:31,166
Same old trick again?

43
00:05:31,791 --> 00:05:33,916
Spit it out!

44
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:36,250
Fuck you.

45
00:06:22,583 --> 00:06:24,208
I know I don't have much choice.

46
00:06:24,791 --> 00:06:26,166
But I don't think I'd win.

47
00:06:26,916 --> 00:06:27,791
I want you all in on this.

48
00:06:28,375 --> 00:06:32,125
I didn't choose you
for being young and a good fighter.

49
00:06:32,708 --> 00:06:33,541
Why did you choose me?

50
00:06:34,083 --> 00:06:37,916
You can save those innocent people.
It's all up to you.

51
00:06:40,833 --> 00:06:42,916
When I win,
we'll make your wish come true.

52
00:06:52,458 --> 00:06:53,875
How many have you hidden?

53
00:07:12,166 --> 00:07:14,875
I swallowed one just now.
Got four in my stomach.

54
00:07:14,958 --> 00:07:17,375
See for yourself
how many dragons are inside me.

55
00:07:30,208 --> 00:07:33,250
I can't beat you,
but I can destroy the demonic liver.

56
00:08:28,166 --> 00:08:30,500
You really don't know what's good for you.

57
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:36,041
You'd rather burn to death
than be my agent.

58
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:39,791
I'll ask you one last time.

59
00:08:40,875 --> 00:08:41,708
Will you

60
00:08:41,791 --> 00:08:43,791
be my agent?

61
00:08:44,833 --> 00:08:49,666
Or would you rather have
everyone here die along with you?

62
00:08:52,291 --> 00:08:53,666
Fall back. Now.

63
00:08:56,458 --> 00:08:58,541
Fuck! I'm one of you!

64
00:08:58,625 --> 00:09:02,166
The golden spells aren't working anymore.
They're about to get in.

65
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:03,166
It's okay.

66
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:04,916
They're everywhere.

67
00:09:08,208 --> 00:09:09,500
Hang in there, everyone!

68
00:09:15,875 --> 00:09:16,916
Who are you?

69
00:09:19,708 --> 00:09:22,125
-I've never seen you before.
-Yeah, who are you?

70
00:09:22,208 --> 00:09:23,791
-It's Leafy.
-The red ghost!

71
00:09:35,291 --> 00:09:36,208
Leafy!

72
00:09:38,791 --> 00:09:40,958
Stop her! She's lifting the spell!

73
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:44,375
Sis Lo! Get the golden ink!

74
00:09:49,541 --> 00:09:50,541
Move!

75
00:09:58,375 --> 00:09:59,708
Go find Han Chieh!

76
00:10:19,375 --> 00:10:20,250
Release him!

77
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:46,791
Was it you, weakling,
who killed my hellspawn?

78
00:11:01,916 --> 00:11:03,375
You're in over your head.

79
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:30,625
You decided to show up, little punk.

80
00:12:32,041 --> 00:12:36,250
I thought you hated
these lousy sacks of skin?

81
00:12:36,916 --> 00:12:39,291
What? Feeling desperate?

82
00:12:39,375 --> 00:12:40,500
Demon King.

83
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,583
How many times have I told you?

84
00:12:44,083 --> 00:12:46,625
You eat like a filthy pig. It's gross.

85
00:12:46,708 --> 00:12:50,041
Can't kill you on an empty stomach!

86
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:55,750
All these years, I've been imagining

87
00:12:55,833 --> 00:12:58,791
how I'm gonna chop off your arms,
break your legs,

88
00:12:58,875 --> 00:13:00,541
tear you to pieces

89
00:13:00,625 --> 00:13:02,708
and finally get my vengeance.

90
00:13:04,708 --> 00:13:05,541
Fine.

91
00:13:06,541 --> 00:13:09,333
So when are we going to screw
those heavenly rules

92
00:13:09,416 --> 00:13:11,583
and have a proper fight
using our true forms?

93
00:13:11,666 --> 00:13:12,791
Soon.

94
00:13:12,875 --> 00:13:15,875
When I've devoured
every soul in the Human Realm,

95
00:13:15,958 --> 00:13:19,208
I'll become more powerful than the gods

96
00:13:19,875 --> 00:13:23,125
and rule over heaven, earth and hell.

97
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,166
Not in this lifetime.

98
00:15:15,250 --> 00:15:16,625
Damn it.

99
00:15:17,125 --> 00:15:20,291
Wu Tien-chi's body is too weak.

100
00:15:20,375 --> 00:15:22,708
Otherwise, I'd easily defeat you.

101
00:15:22,791 --> 00:15:25,541
You're complaining
about using a human body.

102
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:28,375
Then why not use your true form?

103
00:15:30,458 --> 00:15:32,666
If I use my true form,

104
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:35,041
your agent from above will die.

105
00:15:35,125 --> 00:15:36,750
Could you live with that?

106
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:39,625
Demon King,
you're on the verge of defeat.

107
00:15:39,708 --> 00:15:42,208
So you want to provoke me
into using my true form

108
00:15:42,291 --> 00:15:45,125
and violating the heavenly rule?

109
00:15:46,625 --> 00:15:49,541
I've already committed countless sins.

110
00:15:49,625 --> 00:15:51,166
But you're different.

111
00:15:51,791 --> 00:15:54,666
Violate the heavenly rule
and you'll be in deep trouble.

112
00:15:55,250 --> 00:15:58,333
You're too rebellious.
The gods will make you pay.

113
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,041
Hey.

114
00:16:01,666 --> 00:16:05,333
Who do you think
channeled my spirit down here?

115
00:16:15,875 --> 00:16:18,916
The gods think I'm rebellious?
That's just for show.

116
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:21,375
In private, they actually adore me.

117
00:16:21,875 --> 00:16:24,916
You gods are all hypocrites.

118
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,458
Trying to play good cop, bad cop with me.

119
00:16:28,250 --> 00:16:30,208
The righteous path is hard to walk.

120
00:16:30,291 --> 00:16:31,791
So the gods

121
00:16:31,875 --> 00:16:35,458
must be even more ruthless than demons.

122
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:52,708
You little punk.

123
00:16:52,791 --> 00:16:55,291
Your agent from above
may be one in a million,

124
00:16:55,375 --> 00:16:57,166
but there are far more evil people

125
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:00,666
than good in the Human Realm.

126
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:02,416
Cut the crap.

127
00:17:05,333 --> 00:17:10,250
Sooner or later I will defeat you,
Third Crown Prince.

128
00:17:10,333 --> 00:17:13,875
You're a lousy fighter,
but a pretty good escape artist.

129
00:17:26,375 --> 00:17:28,208
Please, have mercy on me.

130
00:17:29,958 --> 00:17:30,791
Give me a chance.

131
00:17:31,541 --> 00:17:33,791
I… I will mend my ways.

132
00:17:34,583 --> 00:17:36,041
I will do your bidding.

133
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:39,208
I… I'll help you…

134
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:44,291
You've been
a real pain in my ass recently.

135
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:48,083
You know all those privileges
the Demon King promised you in hell?

136
00:17:48,166 --> 00:17:49,916
I've taken care of them for you.

137
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,125
They're all gone.

138
00:17:55,458 --> 00:17:58,583
You must know what you deserve.

139
00:17:59,083 --> 00:18:00,375
Do me a favor.

140
00:18:01,041 --> 00:18:01,875
Jump.

141
00:18:11,833 --> 00:18:13,375
I can't go to hell, wait.

142
00:18:13,458 --> 00:18:14,583
I can't go to hell.

143
00:18:14,666 --> 00:18:17,375
Third Crown Prince, I beg you.
Give me another chance.

144
00:18:17,458 --> 00:18:20,083
Give me another chance. I beg you.

145
00:18:20,166 --> 00:18:22,208
Please, I really can't go to hell now.

146
00:18:22,291 --> 00:18:25,041
The gods have already
given you so many chances.

147
00:18:25,625 --> 00:18:28,375
But you always choose the most evil path.

148
00:18:29,583 --> 00:18:32,875
You brought this on yourself.
I can't help you.

149
00:18:36,791 --> 00:18:38,833
Han Chieh is a sinner.

150
00:18:39,333 --> 00:18:42,208
But he spent over ten years
atoning for his sins.

151
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:45,500
He's even willing
to sacrifice himself to save others.

152
00:18:46,250 --> 00:18:47,333
What about you?

153
00:19:14,166 --> 00:19:15,000
Bad boy.

154
00:19:18,541 --> 00:19:21,625
Humans should deal with their own affairs.

155
00:20:03,958 --> 00:20:05,416
This old man again?

156
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:10,166
Unsanctioned revenge
gets you punishment down there too.

157
00:20:17,125 --> 00:20:19,125
COMMAND

158
00:20:21,166 --> 00:20:23,166
A Black Command Token?

159
00:20:23,250 --> 00:20:25,250
Sorry. It's all above board.

160
00:20:32,291 --> 00:20:35,083
The gods have already
given you so many chances.

161
00:20:35,166 --> 00:20:36,541
You brought this on yourself.

162
00:20:44,791 --> 00:20:45,833
You're Wu Meng-hsueh?

163
00:20:45,916 --> 00:20:46,750
PURE EVIL

164
00:20:46,833 --> 00:20:48,000
You are…

165
00:20:48,083 --> 00:20:49,458
I'm Ox Head.

166
00:20:50,041 --> 00:20:51,958
Ox Head? Then this must be…

167
00:20:52,041 --> 00:20:55,041
Quit with the fucking questions.
Can't you see this is hell?

168
00:20:56,041 --> 00:20:57,208
You'd better behave.

169
00:20:57,291 --> 00:21:00,291
With your record,
you'll be here for hundreds of years.

170
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:18,333
Han Chieh.

171
00:21:20,833 --> 00:21:21,708
Han Chieh.

172
00:21:23,041 --> 00:21:24,083
Han Chieh!

173
00:21:32,583 --> 00:21:33,458
Am I dead?

174
00:21:37,666 --> 00:21:38,833
Kid.

175
00:21:39,708 --> 00:21:41,208
Let me show you something.

176
00:21:47,375 --> 00:21:48,541
Where are my parents?

177
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:57,750
Were they reborn?

178
00:21:59,708 --> 00:22:02,750
They stepped on the Wheel of Life
and were reborn

179
00:22:02,833 --> 00:22:05,541
when you agreed to become my agent.

180
00:22:06,875 --> 00:22:07,916
What?

181
00:22:09,333 --> 00:22:12,000
What you saw down here was an illusion.

182
00:22:12,083 --> 00:22:13,208
I deceived you.

183
00:22:14,958 --> 00:22:16,958
So they didn't suffer in hell

184
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:18,875
because of me?

185
00:22:21,583 --> 00:22:23,083
You're the one who suffered.

186
00:22:39,208 --> 00:22:42,833
Chieh, we're about to be reincarnated.

187
00:22:42,916 --> 00:22:46,291
We won't remember you
after we drink the Soup of Oblivion,

188
00:22:46,375 --> 00:22:49,750
so this is our only chance to say goodbye.

189
00:22:49,833 --> 00:22:53,333
We worry about you
and we're going to miss you.

190
00:22:54,375 --> 00:22:57,750
We don't want you blaming yourself
and suffering needlessly.

191
00:22:59,125 --> 00:23:03,000
Chieh, let bygones be bygones.

192
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:05,500
I want you to know

193
00:23:05,583 --> 00:23:08,708
that even if I don't remember you
in the next life,

194
00:23:08,791 --> 00:23:11,416
you'll always be our beloved son.

195
00:23:11,833 --> 00:23:12,916
Always.

196
00:23:13,666 --> 00:23:15,083
Remember that.

197
00:23:42,208 --> 00:23:45,000
Your parents
may not have raised you properly,

198
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:48,250
but they didn't deserve
punishment in hell.

199
00:23:50,666 --> 00:23:51,916
So right from the start,

200
00:23:52,416 --> 00:23:53,875
I helped them be reborn.

201
00:23:55,166 --> 00:23:56,500
But as you know,

202
00:23:56,583 --> 00:24:00,208
that required pulling some strings.

203
00:24:01,833 --> 00:24:03,000
There's a price to pay.

204
00:24:03,500 --> 00:24:05,208
Your hard work these past years

205
00:24:05,291 --> 00:24:08,250
served as repayment for your initial debt.

206
00:24:09,208 --> 00:24:10,041
Congratulations.

207
00:24:10,916 --> 00:24:12,000
Initial debt?

208
00:24:12,916 --> 00:24:14,375
How much more do I owe you?

209
00:24:18,375 --> 00:24:19,958
Life and death are predestined.

210
00:24:20,541 --> 00:24:22,208
This girl is terminally ill.

211
00:24:22,958 --> 00:24:26,458
Not even I can prolong her life.

212
00:24:29,416 --> 00:24:30,375
I can't save her.

213
00:24:31,666 --> 00:24:32,875
But you saved me.

214
00:24:33,958 --> 00:24:37,291
You were determined to die back then.
I just made the most of it.

215
00:24:37,916 --> 00:24:40,916
Not everyone can become an agent
to pay off their debts.

216
00:24:46,708 --> 00:24:47,625
However…

217
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,958
I can give her a new liver.

218
00:24:54,083 --> 00:24:57,333
Because her suffering
is the Demon King's doing.

219
00:25:14,916 --> 00:25:18,458
This golden liver can relieve the pain
caused by her illness,

220
00:25:18,541 --> 00:25:20,500
but it can't cure her or extend her life.

221
00:25:21,083 --> 00:25:23,791
How long she has left is down to fate.

222
00:25:25,083 --> 00:25:27,541
So she might not survive
even with this new liver?

223
00:25:29,625 --> 00:25:32,083
There's a price to pay for this too.

224
00:25:32,875 --> 00:25:34,208
MILK CAPS

225
00:25:35,208 --> 00:25:37,541
THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S AGENT
IN THE HUMAN REALM

226
00:25:38,291 --> 00:25:39,125
What's that?

227
00:25:40,291 --> 00:25:41,125
Contract renewal.

228
00:25:41,958 --> 00:25:45,125
As I said,
you owe me more than that initial debt.

229
00:25:45,208 --> 00:25:47,666
I, HAN CHIEH, AM WILLING
TO RENEW THE CONTRACT

230
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:50,750
AND BE THE THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S AGENT
IN THE HUMAN REALM

231
00:25:52,666 --> 00:25:54,833
This golden liver is included in the deal.

232
00:25:54,916 --> 00:25:56,666
Final offer. Take it or leave it.

233
00:26:07,958 --> 00:26:09,083
I'll sign.

234
00:26:12,041 --> 00:26:13,250
HAN CHIEH

235
00:26:16,625 --> 00:26:18,875
THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S AGENT
IN THE HUMAN REALM

236
00:26:43,083 --> 00:26:43,916
Remember.

237
00:26:44,416 --> 00:26:46,291
Fumigate it with incense every day.

238
00:26:46,375 --> 00:26:47,666
After 49 days,

239
00:26:48,375 --> 00:26:50,125
Javvy will hatch.

240
00:26:54,250 --> 00:26:56,125
Before that happens,

241
00:26:56,708 --> 00:26:59,416
consider yourself on an extended vacation.

242
00:27:00,541 --> 00:27:02,750
Damn, am I nice or what?

243
00:27:03,750 --> 00:27:04,750
Third Crown Prince.

244
00:27:08,291 --> 00:27:09,750
There's one thing I don't get.

245
00:27:11,625 --> 00:27:12,708
Why me?

246
00:27:18,666 --> 00:27:20,208
You had so many better options.

247
00:27:22,250 --> 00:27:23,791
Why give me a second chance?

248
00:27:28,041 --> 00:27:30,250
FENGYUAN TEMPLE,
MARSHAL OF THE CENTRAL ALTAR

249
00:27:30,333 --> 00:27:31,583
You might not know it,

250
00:27:32,500 --> 00:27:34,625
but I've always been by your side.

251
00:27:37,416 --> 00:27:39,708
When you were little,
you loved riding bikes.

252
00:27:40,208 --> 00:27:42,791
You'd cycle around in front of me all day.

253
00:27:45,875 --> 00:27:48,208
-Chieh, why won't you listen?
-Stop running.

254
00:27:48,291 --> 00:27:52,583
The first time you defied your parents
was when you tried to keep a stray cat.

255
00:27:52,666 --> 00:27:53,750
-Listen!
-I want to keep it!

256
00:27:53,833 --> 00:27:55,958
Don't yell at him like that.

257
00:27:56,708 --> 00:27:58,208
You got your way that time.

258
00:27:59,250 --> 00:28:00,125
Hey!

259
00:28:00,208 --> 00:28:01,041
Let's go.

260
00:28:01,125 --> 00:28:05,791
Your first fight
was defending a classmate from bullies.

261
00:28:05,875 --> 00:28:07,583
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

262
00:28:17,416 --> 00:28:19,750
And on that day that haunts you,

263
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,125
I was there too.

264
00:28:28,583 --> 00:28:30,041
I watched you grow up.

265
00:28:30,625 --> 00:28:32,416
I know the real you.

266
00:28:33,708 --> 00:28:36,083
Even though
you went astray and made mistakes,

267
00:28:36,625 --> 00:28:38,458
you never shirked responsibility.

268
00:28:39,916 --> 00:28:43,375
Who could possibly deserve
a second chance more than you?

269
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:48,458
Do your best. I'm watching.

270
00:29:05,583 --> 00:29:08,041
QIANKUN HOOP

271
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:11,041
FIRE-TIPPED SPEAR

272
00:29:12,125 --> 00:29:14,041
GOLDEN BRICK

273
00:29:14,625 --> 00:29:17,041
RED ARMILLARY SASH

274
00:29:17,125 --> 00:29:20,041
LEOPARD-SKIN POUCH

275
00:29:21,208 --> 00:29:23,000
WIND FIRE WHEELS

276
00:29:24,208 --> 00:29:26,708
NINE DRAGONS DIVINE FIRE BARRIER

277
00:29:56,416 --> 00:30:00,625
DONGFENG MARKET

278
00:30:10,916 --> 00:30:13,000
Han Chieh, here's the lighter you wanted.

279
00:30:46,708 --> 00:30:47,750
Any regrets?

280
00:30:48,875 --> 00:30:49,708
For what?

281
00:30:49,791 --> 00:30:51,541
Renewing your contract.

282
00:30:52,666 --> 00:30:54,416
In the end, Leafy…

283
00:31:01,791 --> 00:31:02,875
No regrets.

284
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:05,750
It was a good deal.

285
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:08,666
At least she was happy

286
00:31:09,916 --> 00:31:11,458
for those last few months.

287
00:31:39,250 --> 00:31:42,125
FROM: LEAFY
TO: HAN CHIEH

288
00:31:45,041 --> 00:31:47,500
How are you doing, Han Chieh?

289
00:31:48,666 --> 00:31:52,166
I'll already be gone
by the time you read this.

290
00:31:53,208 --> 00:31:57,416
This is the last time I'll write so much,
so bear with me here

291
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:59,166
and read until the end.

292
00:32:02,250 --> 00:32:05,125
After I got sick, I often thought

293
00:32:05,708 --> 00:32:08,666
that I should do something
to give my life meaning.

294
00:32:10,083 --> 00:32:13,916
Confused and lost, I went to
Dongfeng Market for the first time.

295
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:17,166
I met you and everyone else.

296
00:32:18,125 --> 00:32:21,875
There, I realized that death
is just another form of existence,

297
00:32:21,958 --> 00:32:23,208
so I stopped being afraid.

298
00:32:23,291 --> 00:32:25,666
A new friend? Won't you introduce us?

299
00:32:26,666 --> 00:32:30,250
I felt so much love in my final moments.

300
00:32:31,375 --> 00:32:34,041
It was the happiest time of my life.

301
00:32:34,125 --> 00:32:35,375
GET WELL SOON!

302
00:32:35,458 --> 00:32:37,041
LEAFY, GET WELL SOON!

303
00:32:37,125 --> 00:32:38,375
LET'S GO ABROAD AGAIN!

304
00:32:38,458 --> 00:32:42,458
Han Chieh, I didn't have time
to do all the things I wanted.

305
00:32:42,958 --> 00:32:45,791
I want someone to do them for me.

306
00:32:46,458 --> 00:32:49,750
Please play some video games
with the old guard for me.

307
00:32:50,791 --> 00:32:52,875
Please be kinder to yourself.

308
00:32:54,041 --> 00:32:57,750
And lastly, I have one small favor to ask.

309
00:32:58,791 --> 00:33:02,458
Please love this world for me
with all your heart.

310
00:33:02,958 --> 00:33:05,125
Even if it can be chaotic

311
00:33:05,208 --> 00:33:07,666
and the gods
don't seem to do anything about it.

312
00:33:08,750 --> 00:33:12,583
I believe what really changes the world

313
00:33:13,083 --> 00:33:16,166
is the hopes and dreams
of ordinary people like us.

314
00:33:26,458 --> 00:33:27,958
I did good, right?

315
00:33:28,666 --> 00:33:34,791
IN LOVING MEMORY OF MY LATE FATHER
CHANG HO-CHENG

316
00:33:34,875 --> 00:33:37,250
-Self-draw.
-A White Dragon? Wow.

317
00:33:37,333 --> 00:33:38,625
Come and have some food.

318
00:33:38,708 --> 00:33:42,541
-Good thing I didn't discard mine earlier.
-You should've done. Why keep it?

319
00:33:42,625 --> 00:33:44,250
You're pretty good at this.

320
00:33:46,625 --> 00:33:49,916
Third Crown Prince,
please watch over my son.

321
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:52,666
Bless him with success at work

322
00:33:52,750 --> 00:33:55,500
and with good health.

323
00:33:56,291 --> 00:33:57,250
Hear my prayer.

324
00:34:04,458 --> 00:34:05,458
Han Chieh.

325
00:34:06,166 --> 00:34:09,791
Would you believe it
if I said there really was world peace?

326
00:34:21,333 --> 00:34:24,333
WORLD PEACE

327
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:29,791
Make a wish.

328
00:34:35,916 --> 00:34:38,083
MARSHAL OF THE CENTRAL ALTAR

329
00:34:39,291 --> 00:34:43,000
I believe
that magic can't overcome divine power,

330
00:34:43,083 --> 00:34:45,125
divine power can't overcome karma

331
00:34:45,208 --> 00:34:46,958
and karma can't overcome willpower.

332
00:34:49,666 --> 00:34:55,041
So the most powerful person in the world
is someone with a wish.

333
00:35:02,833 --> 00:35:09,791
WORLD PEACE, MARSHAL OF THE CENTRAL ALTAR

334
00:35:20,125 --> 00:35:23,666
DONGFENG MARKET

335
00:35:59,458 --> 00:36:00,583
Who are you?

336
00:36:00,666 --> 00:36:02,041
Hello there.

337
00:36:08,958 --> 00:36:09,958
You brought a ghost?

338
00:36:10,041 --> 00:36:14,666
No way, you can actually see him?
I'm impressed, Master Han.

339
00:36:15,250 --> 00:36:16,125
I'm Mr. Li.

340
00:36:16,208 --> 00:36:17,375
-I have some--
-Hold up.

341
00:36:18,541 --> 00:36:20,333
-Mr. Li, right?
-Yes.

342
00:36:22,333 --> 00:36:23,875
MR. LI HIRED A GHOST

343
00:36:23,958 --> 00:36:27,375
TO KILL HIS ELDERS
AND INHERIT THEIR MONEY

344
00:36:27,458 --> 00:36:28,875
KICK HIS ASS

345
00:36:32,333 --> 00:36:33,541
Wait!

346
00:36:33,625 --> 00:36:35,541
I came to discuss business with you.

347
00:36:35,625 --> 00:36:37,666
Shouldn't you ask your boss first?

348
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:46,458
I don't need to ask him.
His instructions have never changed.

349
00:36:46,916 --> 00:36:47,750
QIANKUN HOOP

350
00:36:58,208 --> 00:36:59,083
Eliminate evil.

351
00:37:06,916 --> 00:37:10,500
AGENT FROM ABOVE

352
00:37:25,583 --> 00:37:28,125
Money makes the world go round.

353
00:37:28,958 --> 00:37:31,833
Hell is even more corrupt
than the Human Realm.

354
00:37:32,541 --> 00:37:36,166
All your debts can be paid off.

355
00:37:39,416 --> 00:37:41,708
With this Hell Talisman…

356
00:37:44,333 --> 00:37:46,000
you can alter karma

357
00:37:47,208 --> 00:37:49,333
any way you please.

358
00:37:49,416 --> 00:37:51,666
HELL TALISMAN

359
00:38:08,541 --> 00:38:09,916
Come!

360
00:38:39,875 --> 00:38:41,416
There is somebody

361
00:38:42,375 --> 00:38:43,708
I want you to kill.

